QuestData.Title: The More You Know
QuestData.Description: This whole area is littered with Zandalari artifacts. I would be lying if I said studying them didn't interest me. I am fascinated by the significance of these objects to their rituals.$b$bThe more we understand our enemies, the better prepared we are to defeat them.$b$bIf I am to study them, I will need to see them up close. Bring me as many artifacts as you can find.
QuestData.LogDescription: Retrieve 6 Ritual Artifacts from around Conqueror's Terrace.
